https://hackernoon.com/ethereum-development-walkthrough-part-2-truffle-ganache-geth-and-mist-8d6320e12269

For development:

A) Install Ganache

B) truffle compile
   truffle migrate --network develop

For TestNet

a) Install Geth and Mist

geth --datadir=./chaindata/ init ./genesis.json
geth --datadir=./chaindata/ --rpc
open -a /Applications/Mist.app --args --rpc /Users/suresh/Badla/BadlaProject/chaindata/geth.ipc

To attach to geth

geth attach ipc://Users/suresh/Badla/BadlaProject/chaindata/geth.ipc

b) truffle compile
   truffle migrate --network testnet
